short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Step into the mystical allure of a silent forest cloaked in dense fog.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tall trees stand motionless, their silhouettes fading in and out of the mist, creating a serene and enchanting atmosphere. The forest is shrouded in a veil of mystery, evoking the feeling of entering a fairytale world where every sound is hushed, and nature whispers its own hidden stories. This background is perfect for those who appreciate the raw, quiet beauty of nature enveloped in early morning fog.
